Comment: Items: will (Wand of Illusion), Ubertip (Tooltip - Extended)
Value: Create an illusory double of the targeted unit when used. The illusory double deals no damage to enemy units, takes <AIil,DataB1> times the damage from enemy attacks, and will disappear after <AIil,Dur1> seconds or when its hit points reach zero.  |nIllusion lasts 60 seconds.
